               History of changes to pytest-dependency
               =======================================

* Version 0.2.0 (not yet released)

** New features

 + Issue #2: Add documentation.

 + Issue #4: Add a depend() function to add a dependency to a test at
   runtime.

* Version 0.1.0 (2017-01-29)

